| Platform | Build Command | Output Dir | Root | Routing |
|----------|--------------|------------|------|---------|
| **Vercel** | `npm run build` | dist | `.` | vercel.json ‚úÖ |
| **Cloudflare** | `npm run build` | dist | `.` | `_redirects` ‚ö†Ô∏è |
