also add this one more project on projects page https://theoldregime.social/projects{Bitcoin Signet Monitoring Stack

A comprehensive monitoring solution for Bitcoin Signet nodes using Grafana Alloy, Loki, and Grafana. This project implements a complete observability stack with automated deployment, advanced alerting, and professional-grade monitoring capabilities.
Project Overview

This repository contains a production-ready Bitcoin Signet monitoring implementation that fulfills all requirements of the Luganodes technical assessment. The solution provides real-time log collection, storage, visualization, and alerting for Bitcoin node operations.
Key Features

    Complete Bitcoin Signet Node Setup with optimized configuration
    Real-time Log Collection using Grafana Alloy
    Centralized Log Storage with Loki aggregation
    Advanced Visualization through Grafana dashboards
    Comprehensive Alerting with 7 critical monitoring rules
    Automated Deployment using Docker Compose and Ansible
    Professional Documentation with setup and troubleshooting guides

Quick Start
Prerequisites

    Docker (20.10+) and Docker Compose (2.0+)
    4GB RAM minimum, 8GB recommended
    10GB available disk space
    Internet connection for Bitcoin Signet synchronization

One-Command Deployment

git clone https://github.com/oldregime/luganode2025.git
cd luganode2025/luganode25
docker compose up -d

Access Points

    Grafana Dashboard: http://localhost:3000 (admin/luganodes2024)
    Bitcoin RPC: http://localhost:38332
    Loki Logs: http://localhost:3100
    Alloy Monitoring: http://localhost:12345

Repository Structure

luganode25/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ ansible/                    # Infrastructure automation
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ playbooks/             # Deployment playbooks
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ roles/                 # Modular components
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ inventories/           # Environment configurations
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ configs/                   # Service configurations
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ bitcoin/               # Bitcoin Signet settings
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ alloy/                 # Log collection setup
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ loki/                  # Log aggregation config
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ grafana/               # Dashboards and alerts
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ documentation/             # Comprehensive guides
